            <h2>So much gooood</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="card-details">
            <p>Estimated time: 4 hours - Posted 57 minutes ago</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-description">
            <p>I need to paint two rooms. What more do you need to know? Oh yeah, I’d like one room to be a soft blue - the other can be some creamy pasty pink or whatever makes you feel giddy. I’m just a guy who’s tired of white.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-payment">Client Payment: Verified
          </div>
          <div class="card-location">
            <p><i class="fa fa-map-marker" aria-hidden="true"></i> Barcelona, España</p>
          </div>
          <a class="card-link" href="#" ></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3" style="margin-top: 50px">
        <div class="myprofile">
          <div class="myprofile-header">
            <%= image_tag "http://kitt.lewagon.com/placeholder/users/ssaunier", class: "avatar"%>
            <%= link_to "My Profile", dashboard_workers_path, class: "" %>
          </div>
          <div class="myprofile-visibility">
            <h3>Visibility</h3>
            <i class="fa fa-globe" aria-hidden="true"></i><a>Public</a>
          </div>
          <div class="myprofile-availibility">
